ISOGEN-FILES ISOGEN.FLS
UNITS-BORE MM
UNITS-CO-ORDS MM

MESSAGE-SQUARE
    PIPE, LENGTH=1000MM, RefNo:=1, SeqNo:=1
PIPE
    END-POINT 0 0 0 100
    END-POINT 1000 0 0 100
    COMPONENT-ATTRIBUTE1 TEST

